# =============================================================================
# GreenLang Climate OS - Code Owners
# INFRA-007: Repository Governance & Ownership Mapping
# =============================================================================
#
# This file defines code ownership for automatic review assignment.
# Requires at least 1 approval from code owner team.
#
# Rules are evaluated bottom-to-top; the last matching pattern takes
# precedence. Global fallback is listed first so that every PR has at
# least one required reviewer.
#
# Reference: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
# =============================================================================

